name: Buffalo
description: I took this picture somewhere between   Walsenburg and Colorado Springs.   I was in the middle of nowhere, and this buffalo where rooming around this old construction.  Usually, I would have walked close to the animals, but this was an open road, and the herd was far away behind a small creek and a wired fence chilling, eating, and playing.  All I could do was use my long lens and my windows as a tripod to take as many photos as possible.
